\c 27
\s Induna zabantu
\p
\v 1 Njalo abantwana bakoIsrayeli ngenani labo, inhloko zaboyise, lezinduna zezinkulungwane lezamakhulu, leziphathamandla zabo ezazisebenzela inkosi ezindabeni zonke zezigaba, ezazingena ziphuma inyanga ngenyanga enyangeni zonke zomnyaka; leso lalesosigaba sasilezinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lane.
\v 2 Phezu kwesigaba sokuqala ngenyanga yokuqala kwakunguJashobeyamu indodana kaZabidiyeli; lesigabeni sakhe kwakulezinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lane\x + 11.11.\x*.
\v 3 Wayengowamadodana kaPerezi, inhloko yabo bonke abaphathi bebutho ngenyanga yokuqala\x + Nani 26.20. Gen. 38.29.\x*.
\v 4 Laphezu kwesigaba senyanga yesibili kwakunguDodayi umAhohi; l\add e\add*sigab\add eni\add* sakhe uMikilothi laye wayeyinduna; lesigabeni sakhe kwakulezinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lane.
\v 5 Induna yesithathu yebutho ngenyanga yesithathu yayinguBhenaya indodana kaJehoyada umpristi omkhulu; lesigabeni sakhe kwakulezinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lane\x + 2 Sam. 8.18.\x*.
\v 6 UBhenaya lo wayeliqhawe labangamatshumi amathathu, laphezu kwabangamatshumi amathathu. La\add ku\add*sigaba sakhe kwakuloAmizabadi indodana yakhe\x + 11.24,25. 2 Sam. 23.20,22,23.\x*.
\v 7 Eyesine ngenyanga yesine yayinguAsaheli umfowabo kaJowabi\x + 2.16. 11.26. 2 Sam. 2.18. 3.30. 23.24.\x*, loZebhadiya indodana yakhe emva kwakhe; lesigabeni sakhe kwakulezinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lane\x + 2 Sam. 2.23.\x*.
\v 8 Eyesihlanu ngenyanga yesihlanu yayingumphathi uShamihuthi\x + 11.27. 2 Sam. 23.25.\x* umIzira\x + 27.8,13. Gen. 38.30. Nani 26.20.\x*; lesigabeni sakhe kwakulezinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lane.
\v 9 Eyesithupha ngenyanga yesithupha yayinguIra indodana kaIkheshi umThekhowa; lesigabeni sakhe kwakulezinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lane\x + 11.28.\x*.
\v 10 Eyesikhombisa ngenyanga yesikhombisa yayinguHelezi umPheloni wamadodana akoEfrayimi; lesigabeni sakhe kwakulezinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lane\x + 11.27.\x*.
\v 11 Eyesificaminwembili ngenyanga yesificaminwembili yayinguSibekayi\x + 11.29. 20.4. 2 Sam. 21.18. 2 Sam. 23.27.\x* umHushathi\x + 4.4.\x* wabakoZera\x + 27.8,13. Gen. 38.30. Nani 26.20.\x*; lesigabeni sakhe kwakulezinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lane\x + 11.28.\x*.
\v 12 Eyesificamunwemunye ngenyanga yesificamunwemunye yayinguAbiyezeri umAnathothi wabakoBhenjamini; lesigabeni sakhe kwakulezinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lane.
\v 13 Eyetshumi ngenyanga yetshumi yayinguMaharayi umNetofa\x + 11.30.\x* wabakoZera\x + 27.8,13. Gen. 38.30. Nani 26.20.\x*; lesigabeni sakhe kwakulezinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lane.
\v 14 Eyetshumi lanye ngenyanga yetshumi lanye yayinguBhenaya umPirathoni wabantwana bakoEfrayimi; lesigabeni sakhe kwakulezinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lane\x + 11.31.\x*.
\v 15 Eyetshumi lambili ngenyanga yetshumi lambili yayinguHelidayi umNetofa wakoOthiniyeli; lesigabeni sakhe kwakulezinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lane\x + 4.13. Hlu. 1.13. 3.9.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Laphezu kwezizwe zakoIsrayeli: Umbusi wabakoRubeni kwakunguEliyezeri indodana kaZikiri. KwabakoSimeyoni, uShefethiya indodana kaMahaka.
\v 17 KwabakoLevi, uHashabhiya indodana kaKemuweli\x + 26.30.\x*; kwabakoAroni, uZadoki\x + 24.3.\x*.
\v 18 KoJuda, uElihu wabafowabo bakaDavida. KoIsakari, uOmri indodana kaMikayeli.
\v 19 KoZebuluni, uIshmaya indodana kaObhadiya. KoNafithali, uJerimothi indodana kaAziriyeli.
\v 20 Ebantwaneni bakoEfrayimi, uHosheya indodana kaAzaziya. Engxenyeni eyodwa kwezimbili yesizwe sakoManase, uJoweli indodana kaPhedaya.
\v 21 Engxenyeni eyodwa kwezimbili yakoManase eGileyadi, uIdo indodana kaZekhariya\x + 1 Kho. 4.14.\x*. KoBhenjamini, uJahasiyeli indodana kaAbhineri\x + 2 Sam. 2.8.\x*.
\v 22 KoDani, uAzareli indodana kaJerohamu. Laba babeyiziphathamandla zezizwe zakoIsrayeli\x + 28.1.\x*.
\p
\v 23 Kodwa uDavida kathathanga inani lalabo abaleminyaka engamatshumi amabili langaphansi, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* yayithe izakwengeza uIsrayeli njengezinkanyezi zamazulu\x + Gen. 15.5.\x*.
\v 24 UJowabi indodana kaZeruya waqalisa ukubala, kodwa kaqedanga\x + 21.5.\x*; ngoba kwaba khona ulaka phezu kukaIsrayeli ngenxa yalokho; ngakho inani kalifakwanga\f + \fk kalifakwanga: \fl Heb. \fq kalenyukanga.\f* ekulandiseni kwemilando yenkosi uDavida\x + 21.7. 2 Sam. 24.5-15.\x*.
\p
\v 25 Laphezu kwezinto eziligugu zenkosi kwakuloAzimavethi indodana kaAdiyeli\x + 11.33. 2 Sam. 23.31.\x*; laphezu kwezinto eziligugu ensimini, emizini, lemizaneni, lezinqabeni kwakuloJonathani indodana kaUziya.
\v 26 Laphezu kwabenza umsebenzi wensimu, wokulinywa komhlabathi, kwakuloEziri indodana kaKelubi.
\v 27 Laphezu kwezivini kwakuloShimeyi umRama\x + Josh. 18.25.\x*. Laphezu kokwezivini eziphaleni zewayini kwakuloZabidi umShefama\x + 1 Sam. 30.28.\x*.
\v 28 Laphezu kwezihlahla zemihlwathi lemikhiwa yesikhamore\x + 1 Kho. 10.27. 2 Lan. 1.15. 9.27. Hlab. 78.47. Luka 19.4.\x* ezisesihotsheni kwakuloBhali-Hanani umGederi. Laphezu kweziphala zamafutha kwakuloJowashi\x + Josh. 12.13.\x*.
\v 29 Laphezu kwezinkomo ezazisidla eSharoni kwakuloShitirayi umSharoni. Laphezu kwezinkomo ezazisezigodini kwakuloShafati indodana kaAdilayi\x + 5.16. Josh. 12.18.\x*.
\v 30 Laphezu kwamakamela kwakuloObili umIshmayeli\x + Gen. 37.25.\x*. Laphezu kwabobabhemikazi kwakuloJehideya\x + 5.21. Gen. 36.24. Nani 31.34. Neh. 7.69.\x* umMeronothi\x + Neh. 3.7.\x*.
\v 31 Laphezu kwemihlambi kwakuloJaziri umHagiri\x + 5.10.\x*. Bonke labo babengabaphathi bempahla inkosi uDavida ayelayo.
\v 32 UJonathani, uyise omdala kaDavida, wayengumeluleki, indoda ehlakaniphileyo, njalo wayengumbhali; loJehiyeli indodana kaHakimoni wayelabantwana benkosi.
\v 33 Njalo uAhithofeli wayengumeluleki wenkosi\x + 2 Sam. 15.12.\x*, loHushayi\x + 2 Sam. 15.37.\x* umArki\x + Josh. 16.2.\x* wayengumngane wenkosi\x + 2 Sam. 15.37.\x*.
\v 34 Lemva kukaAhithofeli kwakuloJehoyada indodana kaBhenaya\x + 27.5.\x* loAbhiyatha\x + 24.6.\x*. Lomphathi webutho lenkosi kwakunguJowabi\x + 2 Sam. 2.32.\x*.